<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-0978fff0c5acf5a6809afc9a44d3a2e5b24c5eca">The Battle Axe of Balli Stonehand (3d8) (+8,+11) [+5]</h2>
<em>The twin blades of this weapon were forged in Belegost, and powerful forces to resist and endure lie ready for he who shall wield it once more.</em> <p>
It can be wielded two-handed. It increases your strength,  constitution and stealth by 3. It is especially deadly against orcs.  It is especially deadly against trolls. It strikes at demons with holy wrath. It provides immunity to paralysis. It provides resistance to acid, electricity, fire, cold and blindness. It allows you to levitate. It allows you to see invisible monsters. It allows you to sense the presence of non-living things. It speeds your regenerative powers. 
</p>
